headline: Citigroup Raises Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (AJG) Target as UBS Maintains Neutral View
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (NYSE:AJG) is included among 13 Best Long Term Low Risk Stocks to Buy Now. On February 2, Citigroup raised its price objective on Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (NYSE:AJG) to $280 from $277. The firm maintained a Neutral rating on the stock. That same day, UBS trimmed its price target […]
